data.description: Amazing opportunity to own this STUNNING 2-STORY spec home in the Lake Douglas Preserve community. This 2016 GEM has over 3,900 SqFt including 6 Bedrooms, 4.5 Bathrooms and a 3 car garage, giving you plenty of living and storage space. This property has picture perfect landscape and gardening throughout the entire elevation surrounding all views of the home. Upon entering the front porch you will find ELEGANT stonework with a CHARMING RED Main Door and Matching Window Shutters. Large tile flooring covers the entire first story giving you an incredible look with an endless amount of space to decorate. Spacious Gourmet Kitchen has 42" cabinets and an incredible walk-in pantry, kitchen island with granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. Located on the first floor is a master suite with accommodating closet space, 2 large living room options and a guest bathroom. The second floor has matching LVP flooring leading up the stairs including all bedrooms and loft area. Upstairs also includes an oversized master bedroom with dual bathroom vanities and walk-in closet. Once outside of your property you walk into a cozy screen covered patio with a beautiful backyard garden. Fenced in privacy with an additional paved porch area. This ideal location is minutes away from the historic downtown Clermont, Clermont Chain of Lakes, Downtown Groveland which is a dream spot for boaters and fishermen. Plenty of activities, restaurants, bars, shopping, water park, lake beach, piers for fishing, cabanas and much more. Close Range to Hwy 50, US27 and the Florida Turnpike. Contact us today for a private showing.
